<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Advanced Lesson - AI Chess Tutor</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/@chrisoakman/chessboardjs@1.0.0/dist/chessboard-1.0.0.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark" style="background-color: #5c4033;">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="index.html">AI Chess Tutor</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
          <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="index.html">Home</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="play.html">Play AI</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link active" href="lessons.html">Lessons</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item" id="navProfileItem"><a class="nav-link" href="profile.html">Profile</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item" id="navLoginItem"><a class="nav-link" href="login.html">Login</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <span class="badge bg-danger mb-2 fs-6">Advanced Puzzle</span>
                <h2 class="fw-bold">The Back-Rank Checkmate</h2>
                <p class="text-muted fs-5">Can you find the winning move? It is White's turn.</p>
                <hr style="border-color: #5c4033; border-width: 3px;">
                
                <div class="card p-4 border-0 shadow-sm bg-light mt-4">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold">The Situation:</h5>
                    <p>The Black King is trapped behind its own defensive pawns. This is a very common scenario in the late game.</p>
                    <p><strong>Your Goal:</strong> Use your White Rook to deliver a Checkmate in exactly 1 move. Drag the piece to the correct square.</p>
                    <button id="resetPuzzleBtn" class="btn btn-outline-secondary mt-2 w-50">Retry Puzzle</button>
                </div>
                
                <div id="puzzleSuccess" class="alert alert-success mt-4 shadow-sm border-0" style="display: none;">
                    <h4 class="alert-heading">🎉 Brilliant Move!</h4>
                    <p>You delivered a perfect Back-Rank Checkmate. The enemy King has no escape squares.</p>
                    <hr>
                    <a href="lessons.html" class="btn btn-success">Complete Lesson</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 d-flex justify-content-center">
                <div class="card p-2 shadow-lg border-0 no-hover" style="width: 100%; max-width: 350px;">
                    <div id="puzzleBoard" style="width: 100%;"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="toast-container position-fixed bottom-0 end-0 p-3">
      <div id="liveToast" class="toast align-items-center border-0" role="alert" aria-live="assertive" aria-atomic="true">
        <div class="d-flex">
          <div class="toast-body fw-bold" id="toastMessage"></div>
          <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white me-2 m-auto" data-bs-dismiss="toast"></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/chess.js/0.10.3/chess.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/@chrisoakman/chessboardjs@1.0.0/dist/chessboard-1.0.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>